This notice proposes to amend the Offshore Airspace Area at Puerto Rico. This action would lower the base of the San
Juan Offshore Airspace Area from 5500 feet MSL to 2500 feet MSL. The intended effect is to lower the base of the Offshore
Airspace Area to provide sufficient controlled airspace for instrument flight rule (IFR) operations, and to create
a uniform base of controlled airspace in the area.



