offering CPN delivery services provide, at no charge to the caller, an automatic per call blocking mechanism for interstate
callers. The rules require that terminating carriers providing calling party based services, including caller
ID, honor the privacy indicator. The Commission found that the costs of interstate transmission of CPN are 

de minimis, 

